    {
      "instruction": "<p>Slice your <strong>portobello mushrooms</strong> into 1cm strips</p><p>Return the reserved pan to a medium-high heat with a drizzle of<strong> vegetable oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>sliced mushrooms </strong>and cook for 10-12 min or until golden</p>",
