      "instruction": "<p>To assemble, spread the <strong>sweet mustard mayo</strong> on the <strong>ciabatta</strong> <strong>base </strong>and top with the <strong>Portuguese-style</strong> <strong>spicy mushrooms </strong>and <strong>caramelised onions</strong>, then finish with the <strong>ciabatta lid</strong></p><p>Serve the<strong> chips</strong> and <strong>salad</strong> to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
